    id: "2314",
    name: "ITT Tech",
    description: "Fast-track tech degrees for working adults—skip the four-year university hassle and get job-ready skills in labs that actually work.",
    industry: "Consumer",
    cause_of_death: "Built a $1.1B empire on federal loan money while lying about job placement rates until regulators pulled the funding plug in 2016.",
